                        "<div style='text-align: justify;'>2. <b>Endothermic Reaction</b>: Reactions in which energy (heat/light/electricity) is absorbed to break reactants. <br> Example: Decomposition of Calcium Carbonate: <br> CaCO3(s) + Heat → CaO(s) + CO2(g)</div>"
